01:16:03.026 --> 01:16:10.064
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

01:16:15.972 --> 01:16:18.639
We can finally go home.

01:16:21.644 --> 01:16:23.644
Okay?

01:16:24.981 --> 01:16:26.681
Please.

01:16:26.783 --> 01:16:28.316
- No!

